Interface TokenisedAtomicTokenSequence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClassificationSolution, Collection<TaggedToken<TokeniserOutcome>>, Comparable<TokenisedAtomicTokenSequence>, Iterable<TaggedToken<TokeniserOutcome>>, List<TaggedToken<TokeniserOutcome>>, Solution, TaggedTokenSequence<TokeniserOutcome>

    public interface TokenisedAtomicTokenSequence
extends TaggedTokenSequence<TokeniserOutcome>, ClassificationSolution, Comparable<TokenisedAtomicTokenSequence>
    A sequence of atomic tokens tagged with tokeniser decisions, from which a series of predicted tokens can be inferred.
